headline: Sysco to Webcast Presentation at the 2024 Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference
summary: HOUSTON, Nov. 12, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Sysco Corporation (NYSE:SYY) today announced that the Company will webcast its presentation at the 2024 Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference on Tuesday, December 3, at 8:00 a.m. ET. The live webcast for the event can be accessed at investors.sysco.com. An archived replay of the webcast will be available shortly after the live event is completed.
